Snake Game Implementation Using Pygame

Experience the classic Snake game reimagined in Python with the power of Pygame. This implementation offers a dynamic and engaging gaming experience, showcasing the capabilities of the Pygame library.

Description:

This Python code brings the iconic Snake game to life, offering a user-friendly interface and smooth gameplay. Through the integration of Pygame, this project delivers a visually appealing and interactive rendition of the game.

Features:

Customizable grid layout and sizes.
User-controlled snake movement with arrow keys.
Responsive collision detection for both self and apple consumption.
Score tracking and display.
Enhanced graphics and smooth animation.
Embark on a nostalgic journey with this Snake game implementation, showcasing the versatility of Pygame for creating engaging interactive experiences.
